> [!NOTE]
> **Stacking** combines LightGBM + CatBoost + XGBoost + RandomForest with a Logistic Regression meta-learner (5-fold CV). Four additional exotic boosting approaches (BrownBoost, LPBoost, Totally Corrective Boosting, LogitBoost) lacked viable modern Python packages, while rule-based GBDR lacked multi-class support.

